A '''magno-neutralizer''' was a high-tech gadget which could be thrown at a small group of [[Droid/Legends|droids]], exploding and somehow deactivating them.

[[Llez]] once used a magno-neutralizer he had gotten from his father to deactivate a pair of droids attempting to imprison his hero, [[Reddjak]].

